  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "chapterTitle": "女神薇拉",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "713337_22_2410-2453",
          "range": "2410-2453",
          "rangeStart": 2410,
          "rangeEnd": 2453,
          "markText": "我始终坚持认为，每个人都需要依次明白两件事情：第一，我将何去何从？第二，我将与谁同行？",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1718759692,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-19 09:14:52",
          "chapterUid": 22,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2410&rangeEnd=2453",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2410&rangeEnd=2453"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_19_2257-2320",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2257-2320",
      "markText": "同学们都认为我很腼腆，这一评价影响了我的自我概念，自我概念又反过来束缚了我的行为。后来我才知道，这种现象叫做“自我实现预言”。",
      "totalCount": 1088,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2257&rangeEnd=2320",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2257&rangeEnd=2320"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_9_2198-2254",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2198-2254",
      "markText": "所以我很想知道，人生有多少是由运气，即偶然的机遇决定的？有多少是由遗传决定的？又有多少是我们自己把握机会获得的？",
      "totalCount": 990,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2198&rangeEnd=2254",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2198&rangeEnd=2254"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_16_4025-4112",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "4025-4112",
      "markText": "多年后我成为一位大学教授，发现只有备课时倾注无数心血，才能在课堂上表现出即兴随意的潇洒风范。那时我就会饶有趣味地想起那位小丑跳水演员，体会他的表演给我带来的启示：工夫在戏外。",
      "totalCount": 938,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4025&rangeEnd=4112",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4025&rangeEnd=4112"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_16_2605-2625",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "2605-2625",
      "markText": "我们可以接受，也可以拒绝，但是别抱怨。”",
      "totalCount": 854,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2605&rangeEnd=2625",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2605&rangeEnd=2625"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_20_2319-2389",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2319-2389",
      "markText": "事实可以被意识形态歪曲，在里维尔形成的盲目的爱国主义，令我们对一些领导人的非道德行为视而不见。我发誓从此以后要以开放的心态亲自了解事实真相。",
      "totalCount": 828,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2319&rangeEnd=2389",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2319&rangeEnd=2389"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_31_762-823",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "762-823",
      "markText": "人们的态度改变之后，行为会随之而改变；但如果想让态度发生巨大的变化，首先要设法激发人们在行为上的改变，态度自然会随之改变。",
      "totalCount": 828,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=762&rangeEnd=823",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=762&rangeEnd=823"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_7_1343-1371",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1343-1371",
      "markText": "伟人的小缺点让他更招人喜欢，庸人的小毛病让其更招人厌恶。",
      "totalCount": 780,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1343&rangeEnd=1371",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1343&rangeEnd=1371"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_41_1355-1448",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "1355-1448",
      "markText": "永远不要抱怨自己手里抓到的牌。从长远来看，好牌、一般的牌和烂牌出现的机会均等。任何白痴抓到全家福都会赢。打扑克的乐趣就在于想办法把手里的牌以最佳方式打出去。如果打法得当，再烂的牌也能赢。",
      "totalCount": 752,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1355&rangeEnd=1448",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1355&rangeEnd=1448"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_18_560-598",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "560-598",
      "markText": "我着迷了，放开身边女孩的手，开始记笔记。那一刻，我失去了女孩，却找到了天堂。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=560&rangeEnd=598",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=560&rangeEnd=598"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_16_3644-3685",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "3644-3685",
      "markText": "他还教我如何像君子一样从容地打好自己手中的牌，打牌和人生都是如此——尽量不要抱怨。",
      "totalCount": 715,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3644&rangeEnd=3685",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3644&rangeEnd=3685"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_46_8355-8389",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "8355-8389",
      "markText": "有价值的实证研究成果一旦与现行政治意识形态背道而驰，就只能靠边站了。",
      "totalCount": 705,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=8355&rangeEnd=8389",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=8355&rangeEnd=8389"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_21_2462-2539",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "2462-2539",
      "markText": "自然地表露自己的情绪和思想，笑看人生的困境与烦恼，乐于解决问题，有开放的心态和无私的爱心，不持偏见，敢于自嘲，有坚定的主见，能无视反对意见坚持走自己的路。",
      "totalCount": 688,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2462&rangeEnd=2539",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2462&rangeEnd=2539"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_11_3438-3480",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3438-3480",
      "markText": "母亲显然并未意识到，平素自己对父亲的慷慨大方横加指责，这会儿倒期望戈尔迪允许她赊账。",
      "totalCount": 650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3438&rangeEnd=3480",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3438&rangeEnd=3480"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_22_2410-2453",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "2410-2453",
      "markText": "我始终坚持认为，每个人都需要依次明白两件事情：第一，我将何去何从？第二，我将与谁同行？",
      "totalCount": 648,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2410&rangeEnd=2453",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2410&rangeEnd=2453"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_48_3024-3121",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "3024-3121",
      "markText": "社会上大多数人终其一生都在自我保护。实际上，我们每一个人都穿着一套行为的盔甲，试图将别人对自己的伤害程度降到最低。但有时我们将自己的真实感受隐藏得太好，不仅别人无从知晓，连自己也被锁在心墙之外。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=3024&rangeEnd=3121",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=3024&rangeEnd=3121"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_9_4571-4675",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4571-4675",
      "markText": "学生们不断自问： “我是谁？”我则引导他们将这一问题重新建构成：“我想成为什么样的人？”一旦找到答案并心想事成，他们一定也会体会到，理想的实现绝非偶然。",
      "totalCount": 624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4571&rangeEnd=4675",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4571&rangeEnd=4675"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_17_1591-1655",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "1591-1655",
      "markText": "担任话筒男的成功经历既对我有所启迪，也令我倍感困惑：什么才是真正的我？该问题增加了如下可能性：有朝一日，我也能成为哥哥那样的人。",
      "totalCount": 600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1591&rangeEnd=1655",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1591&rangeEnd=1655"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_8_535-610",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "535-610",
      "markText": "小孩子们很难想象他们白发苍苍的爷爷也曾年轻过，更没法想象安详如圣哲般的爷爷也经历过焦躁不安和失败的人生。我想让孙儿们明白，爷爷并不是生来就是这么老的。",
      "totalCount": 561,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=535&rangeEnd=610",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=535&rangeEnd=610"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_9_1045-1128",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1045-1128",
      "markText": "就我而言，大部分降临到我身上的好运，恰好是因为我在正确的时间做了正确的事——选择了正确的职业、找到了合适的人生伴侣、结交了有益的朋友和同行。同时我也十分善于把握机会。",
      "totalCount": 558,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713337&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1045&rangeEnd=1128",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1bf32a005ae2791bf06c5b9?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1045&rangeEnd=1128"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713337_37_2364-2438",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "2364-2438",
      "markText": "孩子们之所以能够控制自己的行为，不是因为某个大人告诉他们不能这样做，而是因为他们进行了自我说服，认定这一行为是不好的。自我说服的观点能维持很长时间。",
